Import:
Everything from the folder of six possible images.

State:
What is the background color
What is the current piece
current display

Constants:
Array of the background color options, black or white
Array of the piece options. Red, blue, or none.

Function:

Effect:
Set current display, when current piece moves. Based on background color and piece.

Render:
An image from one of six options. The background color, and potentially a piece.